The '''2018 Oceania Judo Championships''' was the edition of the [[OJU Senior Championships|Oceania Judo Championships]], organised by the [[Oceania Judo Union]]. It took place in [[Nouméa]], [[New Caledonia]] from 6–8 April 2018.<ref>[http://oceaniajudo.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/maquette-fasicule_V6.pdf Event]</ref>

