{{infobox country at games | NOC = BEN | NOCname = [[Benin National Olympic and Sports Committee]] | games = Olympics | year = | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = | location = | competitors = | sports = | flagbearer = | rank = | gold = 0 | silver = 0 | bronze = 0 | officials = | appearances = | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = {{Team appearances list|team=Benin|competition=Summer Olympics|begin_year=|end_year= }} | winterappearances = | seealso = }} '''[[Benin]]''' has sent athletes to every [[Summer Olympic Games]] held since 1980. Under its previous name of [[Dahomey]], the country also competed in [[1972 Summer Olympics|1972]]. Despite appearing in nine different Olympics, Benin has never won an [[Olympic Games#Olympic champions and medalists|Olympic medal]]. No athletes from Benin have competed in any [[Winter Olympic Games]].
