'''Phayao Provincial Administrative Organization Stadium or Phayao Province Stadium''' ({{lang-th|สนาม อบจ.พะเยา หรือ สนามกีฬาจ.พะเยา}}) is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Phayao Province]] , [[Thailand]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Phayao F.C.]]. The stadium holds 2,406 people.
