'''TV Amriswil Volleyball''' is one of four major divisions of '''TV Amriswil''', a sports club located in [[Switzerland]]. The [[volleyball]] division consists of a semi-professional indoor men's team and a number of casual men, women, and juniors teams.

The A-grade men's team has established itself as a top-tier Swiss team in the early 1990s and has continuously finished the Swiss championships in top ranks ever since.

On an international scale, the club has qualified for and participated in European Cups many times since 1995, while various players of the squad represent Switzerland as players in the Swiss national team.

