{{Infobox sport tournament |year = 2015 |name = Ukraine's Strongest Man |image = |location = Ukraine |establishment = 2000? |format = Multi-event competition |purse = change |month_played = <!--Use if still played--> |current_champion = {{flagicon|Ukraine}} [[Kostiantyn Ilin]] }}
'''Ukraine's Strongest Man''' ({{lang-ua|Найсильніша людина України}}) is an annual [[Strongman (strength athlete)|strongman]] competition held in [[Ukraine]] and featuring exclusively Ukrainian athletes. [[Vasyl Virastyuk]] holds the record for most wins with 6 wins.
